**/.DS_Store

# Obsidian UI state — never commit (personal layout, graph positions, theme)
**/.obsidian/workspace*.json
**/.obsidian/graph.json
**/.obsidian/cache/
**/.obsidian/trash/
**/.obsidian/hotkeys.json
**/.obsidian/appearance.json
**/.obsidian/app.json
**/.obsidian/canvas.json
**/.obsidian/plugins/**/data.json

# Scratch canvases
**/*.canvas

# Large L0 binaries — keep PDFs out of git (manifests in raw/ are fine)
**/sources/raw/**/*.pdf
